<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Parasailing</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/sharm-el-sheikh/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Parasailing</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Obțineți o vedere panoramică și admirați priveliștile uluitoare ale orașului Sharm el Sheikh. Plutește în vânt deasupra Mării Roșii infinite, în timp ce o barcă cu parasailing te trezește pe lângă priveliști panoramice uimitoare ale coastei Sharm și Munților Sinai din jur. Poți să faci parasailing la Sharm el Sheikh singur (singur), cu un prieten sau persoana iubită (dublu) sau chiar cu doi dintre prietenii tăi sau membrii familiei (triplu).        <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        Adult (1): 22 $<br>
        Adult (2): 20 $<br>
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Get a birds eye view and take in the breathtaking views of Sharm el Sheikh. Float on the wind above the infinite Red Sea as a parasailing boat glides you past amazing panoramic sights of the surrounding Sharm coast and Sinai Mountains. You can go parasailing at Sharm el sheikh by yourself (single), with a friend or your loved one (double) or even with two of your friends or family members (triple). 
        When:<br>
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>